{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>假设表达式中允许包含两种括号：圆括号和方括号，其嵌套的顺序随意，如（［ ］（））或［（［ ］［ ］）］等为正确的匹配，［（ ］）或（［ ］（ ）或 ( ( ) ) ）均为错误的匹配。<p><p>现在的问题是，要求检验一个给定表达式中的括弧是否正确匹配？<p><p>输入一个只包含圆括号和方括号的字符串，判断字符串中的括号是否匹配，匹配就输出 “OK” ，不匹配就输出“Wrong”。输入一个字符串：［（［］［］）］，输出：OK。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"括弧匹配检验 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>匹配就输出 “OK” ，不匹配就输出“Wrong”。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>输入仅一行字符（字符个数小于255）。<p>","examples":"<input>［（］）\n</input><output>Wrong\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1354","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}